dataset.title: A remarkable new species of the genus Psammoecus Latreille (Coleoptera, Silvanidae) from Lord Howe Island, Australia

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Yoshida, Takahiro, Reid, Chris A. M. (2023): A remarkable new species of the genus Psammoecus Latreille (Coleoptera, Silvanidae) from Lord Howe Island, Australia. ZooKeys 1161: 117-127, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1161.100872, URL: http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1161.100872
